china/diplomacy/article/3258033/crucial-us-china-work-together-treasury-chief-yellen-tells-vice-premier-he-lifeng?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在广州与中国副总理何立峰举行第一天会谈后重申需要“就关切领域进行密切沟通”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 13:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258033/crucial-us-china-work-together-treasury-chief-yellen-tells-vice-premier-he-lifeng?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟跟随美国评估中国在传统芯片领域的主导地位</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258026/eu-follows-us-move-assess-chinas-dominance-legacy-chips?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>布鲁塞尔发起调查，了解其对中国半导体的敞口，这些半导体为汽车和电视等日常用品提供动力，与美国的一项举措相匹配，但该举措遭到了北京的严厉谴责。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 12:14:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258026/eu-follows-us-move-assess-chinas-dominance-legacy-chips?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴董事长蔡崇信表示，中国企业在人工智能开发方面落后美国同行“两年”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3258002/chinese-firms-lag-behind-us-peers-ai-development-two-years-alibaba-chairman-joe-tsai-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>阿里巴巴董事长蔡崇信表示，美国对中国的芯片出口限制“肯定影响”了大陆科技公司，包括这家电子商务巨头的云计算业务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 11:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3258002/chinese-firms-lag-behind-us-peers-ai-development-two-years-alibaba-chairman-joe-tsai-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>即将访华的俄罗斯总统拉夫罗夫称北京的乌克兰和平计划“合理”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258007/russias-lavrov-who-will-visit-china-soon-calls-peace-plan-ukraine-reasonable?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>俄罗斯外交部表示，高级外交官将与中国外长王毅会面，讨论乌克兰、亚太和其他问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 11:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258007/russias-lavrov-who-will-visit-china-soon-calls-peace-plan-ukraine-reasonable?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>南海：随着领土争端的蔓延，北京和河内试图化解分歧</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257985/south-china-sea-beijing-hanoi-try-navigate-differences-territorial-disputes-ripple?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>高级外交官重申对已有 20 年历史的行为协议的承诺，承诺加强贸易关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 10:23:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257985/south-china-sea-beijing-hanoi-try-navigate-differences-territorial-disputes-ripple?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>珍妮特·耶伦在中国：国务卿严厉打击出口，产能过剩问题提上议程</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257994/janet-yellen-china-overcapacity-high-agenda-secretary-takes-swipe-exports?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国的产能过剩几乎肯定会成为即将与珍妮特·耶伦会谈的主要争论点，因为美国财长在其行程开始时就这个问题发表了强硬的言论。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 09:40:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3257994/janet-yellen-china-overcapacity-high-agenda-secretary-takes-swipe-exports?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>南海：专家表示，北京可以采取更多措施缓解紧张局势并与邻国建立信任</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257927/south-china-sea-beijing-could-do-more-ease-tension-and-build-trust-neighbours-say-experts?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>博鳌亚洲论坛表示，中国可以做更多“为了公共利益”的事情，努力与东盟邻国建立信任。海洋环境保护、科学研究和搜救等领域被认为是中国与东盟合作成熟的领域。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 07:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257927/south-china-sea-beijing-could-do-more-ease-tension-and-build-trust-neighbours-say-experts?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>尽管提高了澳大利亚葡萄酒关税，但中国市场并未为全球行业提供生命线</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3257937/despite-lifting-australia-wine-tariffs-chinas-market-offers-no-lifeline-global-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国上月底取消了对澳大利亚葡萄酒的反倾销和反补贴关税，但行业高管表示，市场和国内消费正在努力复苏。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 05:21:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3257937/despite-lifting-australia-wine-tariffs-chinas-market-offers-no-lifeline-global-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国贸易代表团团长在华盛顿会议上提出美国的限制</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257936/china-trade-delegation-chief-raises-us-restrictions-washington-meeting?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中美贸易工作组首次会谈是在习近平和拜登审查峰会协议以改善沟通的进展几天后举行的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 05:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3257936/china-trade-delegation-chief-raises-us-restrictions-washington-meeting?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>台湾地震、中国神似科比、新加坡34岁奶奶：《南华早报》本周七大亮点</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/article/3257809/taiwan-earthquake-kobe-bryants-lookalike-china-singapores-34-year-old-grandma-scmps-7-highlights?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>从台北在地震后拒绝北京的援助，到新加坡有影响力的人在 34 岁时成为祖母，以下是《南华早报》最近报道的一些亮点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 04:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/article/3257809/taiwan-earthquake-kobe-bryants-lookalike-china-singapores-34-year-old-grandma-scmps-7-highlights?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>科技战：英特尔首席执行官表示，70亿美元的损失是夺回美国芯片生产霸主地位的代价</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257915/tech-war-intels-us7-billion-loss-cost-winning-back-american-supremacy-chip-production-says-chief?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>英特尔首席执行官帕特里克·基辛格讨论了科技行业的发展、地缘政治冲突对全球贸易的影响以及领导力经验教训。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 03:19:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3257915/tech-war-intels-us7-billion-loss-cost-winning-back-american-supremacy-chip-production-says-chief?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国城市因清明节禁止金纸销售和“封建迷信”而引发强烈抗议</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3257876/chinese-cities-spark-outcry-ban-joss-paper-sales-and-feudal-superstitions-ching-ming-festival?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>地方政府在清明节期间禁止销售和生产用于祭祖的金纸、灵钱和其他祭品，此举引发了网上争论，并引起了官方媒体对“粗暴”措施的罕见异议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 02:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3257876/chinese-cities-spark-outcry-ban-joss-paper-sales-and-feudal-superstitions-ching-ming-festival?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>